        <p>MicroStrategy Identity is a multi-faceted enterprise solution that offers the best combination of security and convenience for accessing digital and physical assets. The first component of MicroStrategy Identity is MicroStrategy Badge; this product creates a mobile identity on your smartphone that replaces access control tools like keycards, passwords, and security tokens with a unified digital credential that does not sacrifice security. The second component is MicroStrategy Communicator, which provides identity discovery, location awareness, and two-way communication. These features can be leveraged to coordinate activities across a distributed group of users enabled with MicroStrategy Badge.</p>
